+  m_hat=45.7%, CI=[44.5%,46.8%]
+  D_F=[-6.1%,110.0%]
+  R_.95=[14.5%,74.7%]
+  sign=indeterminate, materiality=material, degeneracy=ok, numerical=resolved
+```
